<div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center bg-primary text-white p-4 px-5">
    <a href="/products" class="btn btn-primary">E-Commerce</a>
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
        <a href="/profile" class="btn btn-primary">Mi perfil</a>
        <a href="/products" class="btn btn-primary">Productos</a>
        <a href="/carts/{{user.cart}}" class="btn btn-primary">Mi carrito</a>
        <a href="/chat" class="btn btn-primary">Chat</a>
    </div>
    <a href="/api/sessions/logout" class="btn btn-primary">Logout</a>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center bg-black text-white p-3 mb-4">
    <h1>Chat E-Commerce</h1>
</div>
<div id="chatContainer" class="container d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center mt-5">
    <div style="height: 600px; width: 800px;" class="overflow-y-auto border border-bottom-0 p-3" id="messageLogs">
        <div id="chatPlaceholder" class="d-flex w-100 h-100 justify-content-center align-items-center">
            Cuando t√∫ o alguien en el chat envie un mensaje se cargaran los mensajes anteriores...
        </div>
    </div>
    <div style="width: 800px;" class="input-group">
        <span class="input-group-text gap-1" id="basic-addon1">
            <img id='chatAvatar' style="border-radius: 50%; height: 25px; object-fit: cover;" src="/img/profile.jpg"
                alt="chat-avatar">
            <div id="userName">{{user.first_name}}</div>
        </span>
        <input id="chatBox" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Escriba un mensaje..." aria-label="Message"
            aria-describedby="basic-addon1">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" id="sendMsgBtn">Enviar</button>
    </div>
</div>
<script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
<script src="js/chat.js"></script>